  • public class al_DecisionTreeBooleanLeaf<E>
extends al_DecisionTreeBoolean<E>
    Represents a leaf on the decision tree; no attribute testing is performed, this class merely returns a value. See colored boxes in figure 18.2, page 699, AIMAv3.
    Author:
    Ravi Mohan, Andrew Brown
